Key changes:

label is removed from ToolConfig — the ActiveTool key (e.g. "GENERAL") drives the translation lookup directly via t(tools.contextMode.${displayed})
Both aria-label and the visible <span> now use the resolved label variable
Translation keys are nested under tools.contextMode to stay consistent with the existing tools.name structure





